                            <comment id="14532973" author="hadoopqa" created="Thu, 7 May 2015 16:40:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;-1 overall&lt;/font&gt;.  Here are the results of testing the latest attachment &lt;br/&gt;
